<h1 id="components">Components</h1>
<p>Speed your workflow with the reusable power of components.</p>
<p>A component is an object or group of objects that can be reused multiple times across files.</p>

<h2 id="creating-components">Creating Components</h2>
<p>To create a component, select an object and press Ctrl+K.</p>
<p>You can also right-click and select "Create component" from the menu.</p>

<h2 id="component-properties">Component Properties</h2>
<p>Components have main properties that are defined in the main component.</p>
<p>Component copies inherit these properties but can override them.</p>
